            "body": "Thank you, I'll try to find workaround using `jobsend()` but just to make sure I understand correctly - it'll be possible in the future to do the following:\r\n\r\n```vim\r\n$ vi foo.gpg               \" open an encrypted file\r\n:%term gpg -q<cr>          \" decrypt it in the buffer\r\nEnter passphrase: ***\r\ni bar<esc>                 \" modify the buffer\r\n:%term gpg -c<cr>          \" encrypt it back\r\nEnter passphrase: ***\r\nRepeat passphrase: ***\r\n:w<cr>                     \" save at the very end\r\n```",
